comments: Reid (MIN) places his hand by Horford's (OKC) shoulder and marginal contact occurs prior to when he receives the pass.
Russell (MIN) extends his arm against Williams' (OKC) hip during his drive and contact affects his ability to defend the play.
Reid (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Williams' (OKC) path and some contact occurs as they disengage.
Reid (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Williams' (OKC) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Williams (OKC) briefly places his hand to Beasley's (MIN) side and disengages as they pursue the loose ball.
Diallo (OKC) and Russell (MIN) engage and disengage with one another off ball prior to the inbound pass.
Rubio (MIN) makes contact with part of Diallo's (OKC) hand that's on the ball and slides his hand off contesting Diallo's driving shot attempt.
Russell (MIN) places his arm against Horford's (OKC) side and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the loose ball.
Horford (OKC) establishes himself in a screening position in Edwards' (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
